Many believe Ini Edo might just be the sexiest Nollywood actress. Although, she hasn’t been too active in the local industry, she is still being fondly remembered. The 37-year old Akwa Ibom native is rumoured to have undergone plastic surgery to enhance her curvy shape just like many other celebrity women. Her beautiful face and shining skin would always be remembered long after her final exit from Nollywood. Even with the talented entrants like Adesuwa Etomi and Beverly Naya, many still crave to see Ini Edo’s face. See more images: Source